headline: A Look At Lowe’s Companies (LOW) Valuation As Shares Trade Near Analyst Targets
summary: Lowe's Companies (LOW) has recently drawn attention after its shares closed at $275.85, with returns over the past month and the past three months outpacing its one-year total return. headline: Bosch returns to the Big Game featuring Guy Fieri as 'Just a Guy' to show that "The More You Bosch, The More You Feel Like A Bosch"
summary: For the second consecutive year, Bosch is taking center stage at the Big Game, spotlighting its home appliances and power tools with a new ad featuring Guy Fieri as an almost unrecognizable version of himself. For the first time in his career, Fieri loses his signature look – spiked blond hair, goatee and bold style – and transforms into "Justaguy" Fieri, a brown-haired, clean-shaven ordinary guy. headline: Lowe's Launches MyLowe's Rewards™ Kids Club to Build Stronger Connections with Families
summary: Lowe's is expanding its family offerings with the launch of MyLowe's Rewards™ Kids Club, a new platform that builds on more than two decades of the company's popular Kids Workshops to help parents and kids build skills, confidence and meaningful connections together.
